# Test: ze web starts HTTPS server and responds to requests
# VALIDATES: web interface starts with auto-generated TLS certificate
# PREVENTS: web startup regression (server fails to bind or serve)
#
# Placeholder: the .ci test runner does not yet support HTTPS clients.
# Full coverage is in internal/component/web/integration_test.go.
# This file exists for spec audit hooks. When the test runner gains
# HTTPS support, replace this with a real startup + request test.

cmd=foreground:seq=1:exec=ze web --help
expect=exit:code=0
expect=stderr:contains=ze web
